        <updateDate>2021-09-14T12:32:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Red Light Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to withhold from states allocations of federal highway funds in FY2020 and thereafter if such states enact laws to provide drivers' licenses or other identification cards to aliens unlawfully present in the United States.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
